import Dashboard from "./Dashboard"
import {BrowserRouter as Router , Switch , Route} from 'react-router-dom'
import Client from "../components/Content/Client/Client"


const BaseLayout = () => {
    return (
        <Router>
           <Dashboard />
                <Switch>

                    <Route path="/dashboard">
                        <Dashboard />
                    </Route>

                    <Route path="/client">
                        <Client />
                    </Route>

                </Switch>
        </Router>
        
    )
}

export default BaseLayout
